snippet.title: Bingocat
snippet.description:
I love comedy, technology, design, games, and the internet! I make mainly tech and gaming themed videos. If you have questions about the software I use or the games I play, feel free to ask!

I don't really have an upload schedule; I just upload when I have ideas and time.

Feel free to check out my gaming channel too!

Computer Specs:
-CPU: Intel Core i7-4790K 4.0GHz Quad-Core
-CPU Cooler: Corsair H60 Liquid Cooler
-Motherboard: Asus Z97-P ATX LGA1150
-Memory: Kingston HyperX Fury Black 32GB (4 x 8GB) DDR3-1600
-Storage: Samsung SSD 960 PRO M.2 1TB, Samsung 840 EVO 1TB 2.5" Solid State Drive, Seagate Barracuda 2TB 3.5" 7200RPM Internal Hard Drive
-Video Card: EVGA GeForce GTX 1070 SC GAMING ACX 3.0, 8GB GDDR5, LED, DX12 OSD Support (PXOC) Graphics Card 08G-P4-6173-KR
-Case: Rosewill Challenger-U3 ATX Mid Tower
-Power Supply: Rosewill Capstone 750W 80+ Gold Certified Semi-Modular ATX
-Operating System: Windows 10 Pro Anniversary Edition 64-bit
